OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FA "callous and selfish" killer
OL,7,Fnicknamed Nasty has been jailed for
OL,8,Flife for fatally punching a profoundly
OL,9,Fdeaf young woman in the neck and
OL,10,Fleaving her to die in the street.
OL,12,FDuane Owusu, 36, threw aspiring
OL,13,Faccountant Zahwa Mukhtar out of an
OL,14,Fovercrowded Mercedes car and felled
OL,15,Fher with a single strike after
OL,16,Fattending a rave in east London.
OL,18,FRather than summoning help, Owusu and
OL,19,Fhis friends drove off as Ms Mukhtar
OL,20,Flay prone on the pavement at 4.30am,
OL,21,Fhaving suffered a fatal head injury.
OL,26,@nD@COUnD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/13
