CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FAfter an Old Bailey trial, Owusu was
OL,7,Ffound guilty of murdering Ms Mukhtar,
OL,8,F27, who had worked at the Young Vic
OL,9,FTheatre as a finance assistant.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, Judge Richard Marks KC
OL,12,Fhanded Owusu a life sentence with a
OL,13,Fminimum term of 16 years and six
OL,14,Fmonths in jail.
OL,16,FIn a televised sentencing, Judge Marks
OL,17,Ftold him he had struck Ms Mukhtar with
OL,18,Fa "forceful blow for which there was
OL,19,Fabsolutely no justification".
OL,26,@zD@COU{D@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FDespite pleas by his friends to get
OL,7,Fher help, the defendant had said "no-
OL,8,Fone cares about her" and insisted they
OL,9,Fleave.
OL,11,FJudge Marks said: "I accept you did
OL,12,Fnot know that she was gravely injured,
OL,13,Fnor indeed the injuries were so severe
OL,14,Fthey were unrecoverable, but the point
OL,15,Fis you could not have cared less.
OL,26,@oD@bOUpD@TO]sD@SOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,F"Whatever her condition you were
OL,7,Fcontent to leave her there, flat out
OL,8,Fon her back on her own at 4.30am,
OL,9,Fclearly under the influence of drink
OL,10,Fand drugs, and for all you knew, miles
OL,11,Ffrom home and no means of getting
OL,12,Fthere.
OL,14,F"More callous and selfish behaviour it
OL,15,Fis difficult to imagine."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUwD@YO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
