PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FIn a statement read to the court, the
OL,7,Fvictim's brother Jamaluddin Mukhtar
OL,8,Fsaid: "Zahwa Mukhtar was a daughter,
OL,9,Fgranddaughter, sister and niece, a
OL,10,Fremarkable young woman whose life was
OL,11,Fshaped by both hardship and
OL,12,Fextraordinary perseverance."
OL,14,FHe said his sister became deaf at the
OL,15,Fage of three after contracting
OL,16,Fmeningitis but never allowed her
OL,17,Fdisability to "hold her back".
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@\O]yD@OOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FShe was known for her "constant smile
OL,7,Fand infectious laughter" and had
OL,8,Falways encouraged others to believe in
OL,9,Fthemselves, he said.
OL,11,FHe added: "Her warmth, kindness and
OL,12,Fbelief in the potential of others were
OL,13,Fqualities that left a lasting
OL,14,Fimpression on all who knew her.
OL,16,F"Losing her has left an immeasurable
OL,17,Fvoid in our hearts. A beautiful
OL,18,Fdetermined and loving soul whose
OL,19,Fabsence will be deeply felt forever."
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@XO]sD@KOUxD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FIn mitigation, Michael Borrelli KC
OL,7,Fsaid Owusu was "deeply sorry" for the
OL,8,Fhurt Ms Mukhtar's family must feel.
OL,10,FJurors in his trial were not told that
OL,11,FOwusu had been jailed for eight years
OL,12,Fin 2010 for being the getaway driver
OL,13,Fin a botched robbery in which a
OL,14,FMatalan shop manager was fatally
OL,15,Fstabbed.
OL,26,@oD@POUoD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FHaving been convicted of conspiracy to
OL,7,Frob, convicted drug dealer Owusu was
OL,8,Freleased in 2013, but was on bail
OL,9,Frelating to a fresh allegation of
OL,10,Fsupplying class A drugs at the time of
OL,11,FMs Mukhtar's death.
OL,13,FMs Mukhtar had never met Owusu before
OL,14,Fshe came across his group in the early
OL,15,Fhours of August 16 last year, and
OL,16,Finhaled laughing gas balloons with
OL,17,Fthem in Stoke Newington.
OL,19,FWhen they decided to return home to
OL,20,FDagenham, she had got into the already
OL,21,Fovercrowded car too.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FOn the journey, she had argued with
OL,7,Fone of Owusu's female friends, pulled
OL,8,Fher hair and threatened to stab
OL,9,Fsomeone, jurors were told.
OL,11,FOwusu grabbed her phone and threw it
OL,12,Fout of the car before ejecting her and
OL,13,Faiming two kicks at her face as she
OL,14,Fsat on the pavement, the prosecution
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FWhen she got up, Owusu punched her in
OL,18,Fthe neck, causing her to fall on to
OL,19,Fthe ground, the court was told.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FThe incident was captured on graphic
OL,7,FCCTV footage and witnessed by Owusu's
OL,8,Fhorrified friends.
OL,10,FWitness Paige Allen described Ms
OL,11,FMukhtar pleading with Owusu to stop
OL,12,Fbefore he landed the fatal blow.
OL,14,FShe told jurors: "He was just rage. He
OL,15,Flooked like a monster. His behaviour
OL,16,Fwas just wrong. She just fell. Just
OL,17,Ffell backwards.
OL,19,F"I went to help her but he screamed at
OL,20,Fme to get in the car."
OL,26,@vD@ROU{D@AOU|D@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FOn leaving the scene in Chadwell
OL,7,FHeath, Owusu and his group were
OL,8,Fstopped and searched by police a short
OL,9,Fdistance away.
OL,11,FThey were detained for about 50
OL,12,Fminutes before officers investigated
OL,13,Freports from the public of a woman on
OL,14,Fthe pavement down the road.
OL,16,FMs Mukhtar was found unresponsive at
OL,17,F5.31am.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1776265866
OL,3,C'Callous and selfish' killer jailed
OL,4,Cfor life over death of deaf woman
OL,6,FDespite the efforts of police and
OL,7,Fparamedics at the scene, she was
OL,8,Fpronounced dead at 6.21am, having
OL,9,Fsuffered a fractured skull and brain
OL,10,Finjury.
OL,12,FIn his evidence, Owusu had told jurors
OL,13,Fthat he did not appreciate that Ms
OL,14,FMukhtar was seriously injured at the
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,17,FHowever, Judge Marks said: "He left
OL,18,Fher there thinking only of himself."
OL,26,@yD@\OUzD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/13
